data.description: Welcome to this magnificent 2 bedroom, 2 bath Penthouse.Picture yourself waking up to the waterwaves and being greeted by inspiring sunrises over the intracoastal. In the evenings, unwind in your balcony and embrace the breathtaking sunsets that paint the sky over Singer Island.Nestled within the highly sought-after Lake Harbour Towers East community, this active 55+ community offers 2 swimming pools, a community social room, a barbecue area,  putting green and shuffle board. Anglers will appreciate the convenience of a dedicated fish filet table right at the water's edge, allowing you to savor your daily catch.But the appeal doesn't end there--Nautilus 220, a prestigious development, is underway, just a few blocks away, with condo offerings starting at $1.3 million. Lake Harbour Towers East enjoys a central location, offering easy access to world-class shopping, fine dining, and golf. Discover a life of leisure, and convenience in this remarkable waterfront community. PB airport is only 20 minutes away.
